          "question": "<p><a name=\"336496\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The maximum number of nodes in a binary tree of level \\( k, k\\geq1 \\) is:</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>Data Structures: NIELIT 2016 DEC Scientist B (CS)</b></p>",
